{"word":"G820 - ἄτιμος - átimos - at'-ee-mos - Despised","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄτιμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">átimos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">at'-ee-mos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Despised</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கனவீனமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without honor, unhonored, dishonored"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5092 - τιμή - timḗ - tee-may'/5092\">G5092</a>; (negatively) <i>unhonoured</i> or (positively) <i>dishonoured</i>. May show a comparative degree such as <i>less honourable:</i> - despised, without honour, less honourable [comparative degree].</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}